title: O'Neill Superkini 2012
description:
Do you want to surf, jump and dive in the sea with confidence, knowing your bikini will stay in place? The Superkini is O'Neill's latest innovation in swimwear, made from a technically advanced Nanofront™ fabric. It's scientifically proven to offer 200% more grip, so it will stick with you no matter what the water throws your way!

The contest goes live April19th 2012 -- good luck!
